#: {{ux|fr|On pense que la '''majorité''' des Céphéides classiques pulsent selon le mode fondamental, bien qu'il ne soit pas facile de distinguer le mode d'après la forme de la courbe de lumière.|It is thought that '''most''' classical Cepheids pulsate in the fundamental mode, although it is not easy to distinguish the mode from the shape of the light curve.}}
# [[adulthood]], [[age of majority]]
#: {{coi|fr|[[majorité sexuelle|'''majorité''' sexuelle]]|[[age of consent]]|lit=sexual '''adulthood'''}}

====Usage notes====
While its near synonym {{m|fr|la [[plupart]]}} defers grammatical agreement of verbs, adjectives, etc. to the noun to which it is related, {{m|fr|majorité}} allows agreement with its related nominal or with itself. Each option carries its own nuance of meaning.

